  "mode": "guided_story",
  "screens": [
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s044",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "模型建好了，怎么知道它好不好？",
        "我们需要在测试集上评估。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "accuracy"
      ],
      "id": "s045",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "accuracy"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "最直观的指标是<term id=\"accuracy\">准确率</term>。",
        "准确率 = 预测正确的样本数 / 总样本数。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "accuracy"
      ],
      "id": "s046",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "但准确率有时会骗人。",
        "比如99%的人没有癌症，一个模型只要全判“无癌症”，准确率就是99%。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "confusion_matrix"
      ],
      "id": "s047",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "confusion_matrix"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "这时需要更细致的指标。",
        "用<term id=\"confusion_matrix\">混淆矩阵</term>可以看清细节。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "confusion_matrix"
      ],
      "id": "s048",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "混淆矩阵有四类：真正例(TP)、假正例(FP)、",
        "真负例(TN)、假负例(FN)。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "precision"
      ],
      "id": "s049",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "precision"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "<term id=\"precision\">精确率</term> = TP / (TP + FP)。",
        "它回答：你说是癌症的，有多少真的是？"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "recall"
      ],
      "id": "s050",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "recall"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "<term id=\"recall\">召回率</term> = TP / (TP + FN)。",
        "它回答：真的有癌症的，你找出了多少？"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "f_measure"
      ],
      "id": "s051",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "f_measure"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "<term id=\"f_measure\">F1分数</term>是精确率和召回率的调和平均。",
        "它综合了两者的表现。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "roc_curve",
        "auc"
      ],
      "id": "s052",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "roc_curve",
        "auc"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "<term id=\"roc_curve\">ROC曲线</term>以假正率为横轴，真正率为纵轴。",
        "曲线下的面积<term id=\"auc\">AUC</term>越大，模型越好。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s053",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "为了更可靠地评估，可以使用交叉验证。",
        "把数据分成k份，轮流用k-1份训练，1份测试。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "exercise": {
        "answer": 0,
        "explanation": "召回率 = TP / (TP + FN) = 9 / (9 + 1) = 90%。",
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "options": [
          "90%",
          "10%",
          "约47%"
        ],
        "prompt": "一个癌症检测模型，把10个真正有癌症的人中的9个判对了，但把100个健康人中的10个误判为癌症。它的召回率是多少？"
      },
      "focus_terms": [
        "precision",
        "recall"
      ],
      "id": "s054",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [],
      "type": "exercise"
    }
  ],
  "sequence_id": "step6",
  "source": {
